creator: Yes Technologies
descriptionHtml: Admissionboard app is perfect for Bangladeshi students who are planning to complete their higher education abroad and want to do the entire process by themselves. Students can search for the right program and find most important information about those programs in a single click. Before you apply, you will have to be eligible to apply to that program. You can find the admission requirements information at a glance on our program information screen. Then you will have to upload all necessary documents and apply. Admissionboard will check your application for errors and then forward it to the university within 24 hours. You will receive continuous updates of your application and as soon as the university has made a decision, you will be notified. If you are successful, your admission letter will be delivered to you via e-mail. You will also get access to our detailed video guides to prepare yourself for your visa application. By viewing these guides you will find out exactly what documents you need to submit and how to fill out the visa application form. This way you can do the entire process by yourself.
descriptionShort: University admission and Student visa. Do everything by yourself using this app.
